727772f-b.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - 70th Avenue
727772f-b.text:
Oueens Boulevard, south side, (of the old Hoffman Boulevard),
between Seventieth Avenue (right) and 70th Road (left), showing
John E. Backus' house. The one-story shed at the extreme right of
the house does not show in the 1927 Queens Atlas. This is a set of
four views. An occupant of this house was Jacob W. 2ipp in 1924.
0ther owners were E. Strong, 1852; A. Whitson Est., 1860; A. Backus,
1873; and John E. Backus in 1891.
February 1923.
View 2: April 1923.
View 3: July 1923.
View 4: August 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
